headline: Energy Transition Today - SunRocket and Novel Energy Propel Solar Growth in Sidney
summary: SunRocket Capital and Novel Energy Solutions have reinforced their collaborative efforts in advancing the energy transition by securing financing for a new solar project in Sidney, Maine.
